g.text: Decide on a bar (familiar places, recommendations, special offers)
Prepare for a night-out (dress-up, ID and purse, cash, etc)
Head to the bar (on foot, public transportations, Uber/Lyft, drive)
Head to another bar (on foot, public transportations, Uber/Lyft, drive)
Enter the bar (ID check, check coat, stamp)
Settle at a spot (counter, booth, table)
Check in with the serving staff (if everything was good)
Drink, chat, social, music, have fun
Get the tab (check the list of items)
Get the receipts and credit cards back (split the receipts)
Calculate the tips (assess the quality of service, calculate with the phone)
Sign the receipt (get a pen, sign on the merch receipt)
Put away the customer receipt (purse, pocket, throw away)
Split the bill with friends (Venmo, ApplePay, cash)
